<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1918-06-22T15:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1918-06-22T15:00:00-05:00" n="289" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d289">
                            <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 861.00/2033</note>
                            <head><hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of
                                        State</gloss> to the Minister in China</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_RPS1" type="to"><hi rend="italic">Reinsch</hi></persName>)</head>
                            <opener>
                                <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                            </opener>
                            <opener>
                                <dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1918-06-22T16:00:00-04:00"><hi rend="italic">June 22,
                                            1918, 4 p.m.</hi></date></dateline>
                            </opener>
                            <p>Referring telegram to Department from Consul Harbin June 14<note n="1" xml:id="d289fn1"><hi rend="italic">Ante</hi>, <ref target="#pg_208">p. 208</ref>.</note> recommending
                                publication of written memorial signed by Allied consular
                                representatives, Department disapproves of publication and is not
                                prepared at this time that any of its representatives should be
                                connected with any public statement endorsing military intervention
                                in Siberia.</p>
                            <p>Please advise Tokyo, Harbin, and Vladivostok accordingly.</p>
                            <closer>
                                <signed><persName corresp="#p_LR1"><hi rend="smallcaps">Lansing</hi></persName></signed>
                            </closer>
                        </div>
                        </body></text></TEI>